sourcesContent: import styles from './InvesmentRow.module.css' const formatter = new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US', { style: 'currency', currency: 'USD', minimumFractionDigits: 2, maximumFractionDigits: 2, }) const InvestmentRow = (props) => { console.log(props.savingsEndOfYear) console.log(props.yearlyInterest) return ( {props.year} {formatter.format(props.savingsEndOfYear)} {formatter.format(props.yearlyInterest)} {formatter.format(props.yearlyInterest)} {props.savingsEndOfyear - props.yearlyInterest} ) } export default InvestmentRow
